message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that has the potential to be incredibly valuable to your business. While I can't disclose specifics just yet, I can assure you it's worth at least $800000 to me. I'm confident it will be worth even more to you.  I'm willing to sell it to you for $900000.  This is a limited-time offer, so please let me know if you're interested.
